f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa14cc7339497d0b57ebbb37ce91db43a106bc3","tid":2439126,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d4d6b9d1ab426ef319e075d3059c455ba3a2731","tid":2439126,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"話事話，其實日本運黎香港d野食，係咪真係冇輻射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"超標就唔俾運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece82e2727bef24a4b954b823f16ad5028c163ff","tid":2439126,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ec5a3ecf01b9704f523331b444aa0c5155bf7a","tid":2439126,"uid":325586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:41:52.000Z","msg":"松村直登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a65ce31257076afc83fd45521932c354888d5a","tid":2439126,"uid":260232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d4d6b9d1ab426ef319e075d3059c455ba3a2731","tid":2439126,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"話事話，其實日本運黎香港d野食，係咪真係冇輻射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"搭飛機都有輻射啦"},{"pid":"c70156fb6f54604648cb16856cac4bc506364b61","tid":2439126,"uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n日本福島「貓男」不畏核輻射，住重災區守護「41隻流浪貓」<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n現年57歲的加藤榮原是福島浪江町一間小型建築公司的老闆，在2011年3月11日福島核災後，他一夕之間成為核災區最嚴重受災戶。雖然，日本政府曾於2017年進行除汙工程，宣布解除部分限制區域，但加藤榮的家仍屬於「歸還困難」的限制區，因此他只能「回家拜訪」不能「過夜」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，加藤榮顯然沒有好好遵守這些規定，至今他仍在家中照料多達41隻貓和1隻狗「Pochi」。加藤榮稱他之所以會這樣做，除了浪江町是自己的故鄉外，他不忍心看那些貓狗流離失所。<br />\n<br />\n一個月花費19萬元<br />\n<br />\n加藤榮的一天幾乎都跟貓狗綁在一起，從醒來到闔眼他要做的工作包含：清理籠舍、就醫檢查、準備食物、陪伴玩耍。平時加藤榮會把食物留在裝有煤氣爐，較為溫暖的倉庫內，讓貓咪在裏頭吃飯、取暖。加藤榮分享，幫貓狗買食物、就醫的花費，一個月林林總總加起來大約7000美元（約新台幣19萬元）。此外，由於住所沒有自來水，因此加藤榮必須帶著桶子到遠處打水，或開車到附近的公廁取水。<br />\n<br />\n想照顧這些貓咪直到最後一刻<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透社》報導，這10年來，加藤榮呵護的小貓咪其實已逐漸衰老，部分的貓咪更出現白血病等狀況，現在加藤榮的後院就埋葬了23隻過世貓咪。<br />\n加藤榮說道：「我希望自己可以待在這裡，照顧這些貓咪直到最後一刻。在這之後，我想我就可以安心離開這個世界了，不管是在一天、或是一小時之後。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sMhNfQqE0eH6vxIc5s8XPg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQwMi4xMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMz/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/1g14tClpfqn3wChy8zWtUQ--~B/aD0zNzc7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/taisounds_com_380/a8d1b253c00aa99411f8c8556d5ea6f2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsMhNfQqE0eH6vxIc5s8XPg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQwMi4xMzMzMzMzMzMzMzMz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1g14tClpfqn3wChy8zWtUQ--~B%2FaD0zNzc7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Ftaisounds_com_380%2Fa8d1b253c00aa99411f8c8556d5ea6f2&h=d02ff7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/日本福島-貓男-他不畏核輻射-住重災區守護-41隻浪貓-012000703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A6%8F%E5%B3%B6-%E8%B2%93%E7%94%B7-%E4%BB%96%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%8F%E6%A0%B8%E8%BC%BB%E5%B0%84-%E4%BD%8F%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BD%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7-41%E9%9A%BB%E6%B5%AA%E8%B2%93-012000703.html&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5sm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=9115f36a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/日本福島-貓男-他不畏核輻射-住重災區守護-41隻浪貓-012000703.html</a>"},{"pid":"778e57db5799854d91e2385ee6a37207c7e4fbc3","tid":2439126,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"人間有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces